{
  "stem": "10478.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you took, all together, one shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had to-- to move to get some water on your body.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you had to undress in your cell, because there was lots of fleas there, and then the lice, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you got clean clothes after that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were even worse than the ones we had before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was an awful mess there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not all, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was  in the concentration camp for about three or four months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they sent me to a prison.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To another prison in Utrecht.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there I was to appear before a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A court-- an army court-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Court martial, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] told us that they couldn't find any evidence against me and my friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were dismissed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for our own safety, they didn't let us go, because they were afraid that you're going to start again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So to protect me, you know, they kept me there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the first   prison, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was around September, 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, of course, there came the Allies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They liberated the southern part of the Netherlands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in order to give a good impression, they emptied the  prison for those people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So like me and others, we were allowed to go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about three months in that prison, yet, until October, 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nobody.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only thing I had in that cell was a man who was from the Dutch intelligence service.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I had to appear before the court, the court martial, he had little pills, pep pills.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, [INAUDIBLE] he take one, he said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you'll be more alert, and you know what you're going to say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he said, also, don't answer them in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Act if you don't understand German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that way, you get a translator, and they give you time to think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But as a result of that pep pill, I was answering before the guy was finished with translating everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was OK, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had not enough evidence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] They thought we were trying to liberate a friend, out of the-- Derk Van Assen-- out of the prison.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had no success.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They shot Van Assen, but they didn't want to admit   it there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they acted, you know, he was still rescued, but not by them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The liberation occurred, for me, not in the southern part of Holland, what happened in September, 1944.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it happened to me in May 1945, when I was in Utrecht with-- with some family, [INAUDIBLE] for the second time  I was released from prison.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stayed with some family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- they couldn't stay there anymore, because they had hardly any food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I even met my brother there, who were the two, and he brought me to a farmer about 10 kilometers from Utrecht.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they went-- there we stayed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there, I had the liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Canadian soldiers came on the-- on the road to Utrecht.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The came inside this village there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was an quite a party there, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody scream with pleasure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at all, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought me-- later on, they brought me home to Maastricht.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they entered Maastricht, I go into my own place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] They spread it around to all the Jewish people who we're helping live there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they all came and all run to my house, you know, to show enormous welcome, yeah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was excited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was, to me, that was the crown on my work, let's put it that way, that I helped these people, and that they could walk around as free men and women in the city of Maastricht, again, yeah.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had a part in that, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some member of my family spill it right away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister, I guess, must have done that, right away, to put it back, because we didn't have a telephone at the time, and run out, he's home, he's home.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went to our place, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he embraced me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my whole face was all with lipstick and whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CHUCKLING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A good memory, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all the family who lived there, so there was, maybe, 30, 40 dropped in, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, oh, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at night, there was the [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "G ?] [? corps ?] from band from the community.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came to our place and gave me serenades.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
